Cell.Data: Mikhaila wants to know what happened to her father. Deep Storage has an archive of audiologs - recordings of experiments that took place in Psychotronics. She's asked me to dig up the last entry that matches her father's volunteer number.

I dug up an entry that matched her father's volunteer number and listened to the recording. Mikhaila's father died in an experiment conducted by TranStar scientists. One of the scientists was me. Now, I have to decide if I'm going to give the recording to Mikhaila or erase it for good.
